title: Chinese market goes ‘super bull’ after mysterious screenshot spreads like wildfire

media:group.media:title: Chinese market goes ‘super bull’ after mysterious screenshot spreads like wildfire
media:group.media:description:
A screenshot of four paragraphs about a plan to remove the zero-COVID policy and reopen China made the Chinese stock market rise up like a rocket for two days.
